{
  "texts": [
    "Two different settings of heterogeneous TL were evaluated: transductive and inductive.",
    "In the first scenario, weather conditions, price and occupancy schedules, and thermophysical properties of the building envelope were modified compared to the source building.",
    "In the second scenario, the effectiveness of online TL was assessed when the objective function was modified to include peak shaving.",
    "The online TL framework introduced in this study integrates three key techniques: model slicing, imitation learning and weight-initialisation.",
    "Imitation learning is used to initialise the memory buffer of the target controller with transitions collected during a one-week RBC implementation."
  ]
}